Package: kineis
Title: Library to automate the download of argos data from Kineis satellites
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Curro", "Abascal", , "francisco.abascal@ieo.csic.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The library uses CLS's Telemetry API (documented via OpenAPI/Swagger) to automatically download bulk satellite telemetry data, integrating it into R with httr.
